nodes.text: Dagelin Minor was a planet in the Outer Rim Territories.
98% of the sapient population of Dagelin Minor died of the Hardan plague, brought to the planet by Bogan's brown nafen imported to control the local dhuru fly population.
Sometime between 2 BBY and 0 BBY, Princess Leia Organa of Alderaan led a mercy mission to Dagelin Minor.
